            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "B.D.M International , it's one of the most eminent school in the city of joy , Kolkata. It is fully Air Conditioned and has smart Classroom and Good and Qualified Teachers. It not only focus on studies but also pays a lot of attention towards Cultural Programs and Physical Fitness. It also has Lab, Library, Lift/elevator and canteen facilities. The school has CCTV surveillance all around the school and Staircases. I know bdmi had some ink splashes regarding the behaviour of some students, but to be honest the situation is changing. As a student of this school who is ready for 14 years I would like to say that : Over all the School is a good school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
