            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "BDM International has been  providing  value  based  education  to young  minds since  the last 57 years. The school is  doing excellent  in all the fields especially  giving a lot of  exposure to children. Curriculum  is designed in a way to encourage  students to play,perform,experiment and interact.The school is preparing  the  students in such a way so that  they become  mentally  alert,morally sound and academically  strong. Moreover the school  has committed  teachers who always extend their hands for betterment of the students.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
