          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Lopamudra pal choudhuri"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-07-26",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It is an excellent CBSE school having very good infrastructure. There is a very good library, Science laboratories, Computer lab, big play ground, smart boards which help the students to enjoy their school life. The student centric education system is being followed here. The teachers are dedicated and are concerned about the overall development of the children . The classes are interactive. Apart from studies they are involved with a lot of activities which they enjoy. After completion of the school education they get opportunity to get admission in various reputed institutions in the country & abroad. Hope the school will be one of the best schools in our country in near future.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "B.D.M International - Golf Green"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Gargi Mukherjee"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-07-26",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I have read some reviews from some current and ex-students of this school about how the teachers are money mongers and how pathetic the education system is over here and so on. I passed out from this school only, years back though and I believe if I am able to write even one line of review also it's because my teachers taught me to do so. If I am able to earn a single rupee of salary by doing whatsoever is because of those beautiful teachers who always with a smile solved all our queries. I believe there is good and bad in everything but what we choose to see is our conscience. So dear juniors or seniors who are posting all the negative things here, please try to remember one good thing that you yourself did for this school because a healthy relationship is a two way bridge.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        }
